reviewText: Great story line, a classic with a twist. Great music.
Great movie, fun songs, great values and good story line.
Love this movie! Such a great story for young kids to watch. I teach Sunday school for ages 1-5 and these kids love this movie! The songs are so catchy! Overall highly recommend!
So cute. My 6 year old granddaughter loves it. And it was a great price too. Thank you Amazon.
